Having said that, I am appalled at what she appears to have done to Johnny Depp. I am also appalled at the United Nations remaining silent about their Ambassador for Domestic Violence "for women" (that's a double whammy in my books).  I am also appalled at the mainstream media, metoo, believewomen.

It appears that the same rules don't apply for people who gaslight (mentally abuse) and physically abuse their partners if they lack a penis.
